I JUST WANTED TO TALK TO HER!

00:15.883 --> 00:16.950
JUST DRIVE.

00:16.984 --> 00:18.652
JUST DRIVE.

00:18.685 --> 00:19.720
WHAT'S THIS?

00:19.753 --> 00:21.788
FILING PAPERS...
FOR MY CAMPAIGN.

00:21.822 --> 00:23.757
NOTARIZE THEM,
SEND THEM IN.
SURE.

00:23.790 --> 00:26.326
TABLE FOR THREE.

00:26.360 --> 00:28.395
Conrad: AND I'M JUST SUPPOSED
TO TRUST YOU?

00:28.428 --> 00:30.130
OH, YOU DON'T HAVE
TO TRUST ME.

00:30.163 --> 00:33.467
TRUST YOUR PARTNER,
WHO HAPPENS TO BE MY PARTNER.

00:33.500 --> 00:35.903
