BROWN EYES, AND ME,

00:35.936 --> 00:37.905
I JUST FALL INTO SHIT!

00:37.938 --> 00:38.906
BE MY FRIEND!

00:38.939 --> 00:40.841
LET GO OF
MY FUCKING HAIR!

00:40.874 --> 00:41.842
BE MY FRIEND!

00:41.875 --> 00:43.110
I HAVE TO FUCK YOU.

00:43.143 --> 00:45.546
YOU DON'T HAVE THE QUALITIES
I LOOK FOR IN A MAN.

00:45.579 --> 00:47.915
BUT YOU DO HAVE SOFT SKIN.

00:47.948 --> 00:49.416
