♪♪ LITTLE BOXES ALL THE SAME ♪♪

01:50.210 --> 01:52.980
HELLO.

01:55.082 --> 01:57.985
NOW, I THOUGHT YOUR PEOPLE
DIDN'T EAT COWS.

01:58.018 --> 02:00.153
I THOUGHT YOURS DON'T EAT
CHEESEBURGERS.

02:00.187 --> 02:02.890
WELL, WE'VE SUFFERED SO MUCH
ALREADY,

02:02.923 --> 02:05.125
I FEEL IT'S MY DESTINY

02:05.158 --> 02:07.060
TO INDUCE POSITIVE CHANGE
IN MY TRIBE,

02:07.094 --> 02:08.896
BEGINNING WITH
THE CHEESEBURGER,

02:08.929 --> 02:12.299
PROGRESSING TO EXTREME SPORTS
AND POLICE WORK.

02:12.332 --> 02:14.868
HEY, FELLAS.

02:14.902 --> 02:17.871
WHO'S A GOOD DOGGY?
YES, YOU ARE.

02:17.905 --> 02:19.873
HI, DOGGY.
WHERE DID YOU COME FROM?

02:19.907 --> 02:22.042
FOUND HIM ON THE STREET.
DOESN'T HAVE ANY TAGS.

02:22.075 --> 02:23.243
JUST THIS GOLD NECKLACE.

02:23.277 --> 02:24.912
MUST HAVE BELONGED
TO THE ARMENIANS.

02:24.945 --> 02:26.380
NOT HAIRY ENOUGH.

02:26.413 --> 02:28.182
GET THAT BEAST THE FUCK
OUT OF HERE.

02:28.215 --> 02:29.783
Shh! YOU'RE SCARING HIM.

02:29.816 --> 02:31.018
IT'S OKAY, MR. SWEATERS.

02:31.051 --> 02:33.220
YEAH, WHO'S OUR TOUGH
LITTLE WATCHDOG?

02:33.253 --> 02:34.855
YOU ARE.

02:34.888 --> 02:36.823
[ BARKS ]

02:36.857 --> 02:38.258
OH, MY GOD!

02:38.292 --> 02:40.327
OH, SHIT.

02:40.360 --> 02:41.562
OH, MY GOD!

02:41.595 --> 02:43.030
GET IT OFF ME!

02:43.063 --> 02:44.765
BACK, MR. SWEATERS!
OFF, OFF!

02:44.798 --> 02:47.000
CHEESEBURGER,
CHEESEBURGER?

02:47.034 --> 02:48.335
STICK YOUR FINGER
UP HIS ASS.

02:48.368 --> 02:50.504
WHAT?
I READ IT ON THE INTERNET.

02:50.537 --> 02:51.505
IT MAKES HIM LET GO.

02:51.538 --> 02:53.240
FUCK YOU. STICK YOUR OWN FINGER
UP HIS ASS.

02:53.273 --> 02:55.909
SOMEBODY STICK THEIR FINGER
UP HIS ASS!

02:55.943 --> 02:57.044
UGH.

02:57.077 --> 02:59.313
I'LL DO IT.

02:59.346 --> 03:00.914
[ GROWLING ]

03:00.948 --> 03:02.282
[ DOG WHIMPERS ]

03:02.316 --> 03:06.286
OH, GOD, OH, GOD,
OH, GOD, OH, GOD!

03:06.320 --> 03:07.387
WOW, IT WORKS.

03:07.421 --> 03:09.723
SOMEBODY CALL 911.
I'VE GOT DOG‐DOODIE HANDS.

03:09.756 --> 03:11.758
NO, NOBODY CALL 911.

03:14.027 --> 03:16.730
Andy:
THAT BITCH ATE MY TOES!

03:22.503 --> 03:25.272
Judah.

03:25.305 --> 03:27.841
OH, HEY.

03:27.875 --> 03:30.110
DAD'S COLOGNE?

03:30.143 --> 03:31.745
I FOUND IT
IN YOUR BATHROOM.

03:31.778 --> 03:32.913
I'LL PUT IT BACK,
I SWEAR.

03:32.946 --> 03:34.248
IT'S OKAY, SWEETIE.

03:34.281 --> 03:37.784
JUST NEXT TIME, YOU MIGHT NOT
WANT TO USE SO MUCH.

03:37.818 --> 03:39.520
WHAT REEKS IN HERE?

03:39.553 --> 03:41.755
SHANE HAS A DEBATE.

03:41.788 --> 03:44.892
SO, WHAT, YOU'RE HOPING
TO STINK OUT YOUR OPPONENT?

03:44.925 --> 03:46.727
WE'RE LEAVING
IN FIVE MINUTES,

03:46.760 --> 03:49.696
SO GO PEE AND GET YOUR NOTES
AND THINGS TOGETHER.

03:51.198 --> 03:53.734
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

03:53.767 --> 03:54.868
WHAT NOW?

03:54.902 --> 03:56.570
YOUR S. A. T. SCORES, NOW.

03:56.603 --> 03:58.939
YOU BARELY SCORED ABOVE
WHAT YOU WOULD HAVE GOTTEN

03:58.972 --> 04:00.707
IF YOU'D ONLY SIGNED
YOUR NAME.

04:00.741 --> 04:02.176
IN CASE YOU HAVEN'T NOTICED,

04:02.209 --> 04:04.878
I'VE BEEN
A LITTLE PREOCCUPIED.

04:04.912 --> 04:08.515
YOU TOOK THE S. A. T. s
WEEKS BEFORE THE...

04:08.549 --> 04:09.650
THING.

04:09.683 --> 04:10.684
ABORTION?

04:10.717 --> 04:12.519
THAT.

04:12.553 --> 04:15.989
IT HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH YOUR LOUSY PERFORMANCE.

04:16.023 --> 04:19.193
I'VE SPOKEN
TO MR. WEINSTOCK.

04:19.226 --> 04:20.093
WHO?

04:20.127 --> 04:21.862
YOUR GUIDANCE COUNSELOR.

04:21.895 --> 04:24.765
HE SAYS YOU CAN TAKE
THE TEST AGAIN

04:24.798 --> 04:25.866
IN EIGHT WEEKS.

04:25.899 --> 04:27.868
I AM NOT TAKING
THE TEST AGAIN.

04:27.901 --> 04:29.069
YES, YOU ARE.

04:29.102 --> 04:30.904
SILAS, YOU COULDN'T GET
INTO TRAFFIC SCHOOL

04:30.938 --> 04:32.339
WITH THOSE SCORES.
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

04:32.372 --> 04:34.908
SO? FROM WHAT I'VE SEEN,
YOU DON'T NEED A COLLEGE DEGREE

04:34.942 --> 04:36.777
TO START YOUR OWN BUSINESS,
RIGHT, MOM?

04:36.810 --> 04:39.646
HEY, DOUG.

04:40.881 --> 04:44.585
OH, SHIT,
WHAT KIND OF ACCIDENT?

04:44.618 --> 04:45.886
YEAH, BYE.

04:45.919 --> 04:47.888
UNCLE ANDY'S
IN THE HOSPITAL.

04:47.921 --> 04:48.789
WHAT HAPPENED?

04:48.822 --> 04:49.790
I'M NOT SURE.

04:49.823 --> 04:53.126
SOMETHING WITH A DOG
OR A SWEATER.

04:53.160 --> 04:55.529
CAN YOU TAKE SHANE
TO HIS DEBATE?

04:55.562 --> 04:56.663
YEAH, I'LL TAKE HIM.

04:56.697 --> 04:58.198
THANK YOU.
BUT IN YOUR CAR.

04:58.232 --> 05:00.601
I DON'T WANT HIM
STINKING UP MINE.

05:06.039 --> 05:07.341
HOW IS HE?

05:07.374 --> 05:09.176
HE'S DOING BETTER
SINCE HE GOT HIS MORPHINE.

05:09.209 --> 05:10.811
DID YOU FIND MY TOES?

05:10.844 --> 05:12.179
HIS TOES?

05:12.212 --> 05:13.580
THE DOG ATE TWO OF HIS TOES

05:13.614 --> 05:15.749
BEFORE SANJAY STUCK
A FINGER UP HIS ASS.

05:15.782 --> 05:17.918
WHY WAS THERE A DOG
AT THE HOUSE?

05:17.951 --> 05:20.888
HELLO.
I'M DR. BERTNER.

05:20.921 --> 05:21.855
NANCY BOTWIN.

05:21.889 --> 05:23.724
YOUR HUSBAND?

05:23.757 --> 05:24.758
BROTHER‐IN‐LAW.

05:24.791 --> 05:26.093
IS HE GOING TO BE OKAY?

05:26.126 --> 05:29.096
IS HE A DANCER, PROFESSIONAL
ATHLETE, OR FOOT MODEL?

05:29.129 --> 05:30.664
NONE OF THE ABOVE.

05:30.697 --> 05:32.165
HE SHOULD LEAD
A NORMAL LIFE.

05:32.199 --> 05:34.301
I WOULDN'T GO THAT FAR.
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:34.334 --> 05:35.536
IF YOU'D BROUGHT IN
THE TOES,

05:35.569 --> 05:37.905
