TO REATTACH THEM.

05:37.938 --> 05:39.773
MUST FIND TOES.

05:39.806 --> 05:41.909
CONRAD,
WHERE ARE THE TOES?

05:41.942 --> 05:43.510
THE DOG ATE THEM.

05:45.646 --> 05:46.747
THE DOG ATE THEM.

05:46.780 --> 05:47.948
WELL, THAT'S THAT.

05:47.981 --> 05:50.651
WHEN IS HE GOING TO BE ABLE
TO GO HOME?

05:50.684 --> 05:51.752
DOES HE HAVE INSURANCE?

05:51.785 --> 05:52.819
OH, NO.

05:52.853 --> 05:54.488
HE CAN GO HOME NOW.

05:54.521 --> 05:56.190
HEY.

05:56.223 --> 05:58.225
I DIDN'T MEAN TO BLINDSIDE YOU
WITH PETER.

05:58.258 --> 06:00.093
I JUST KNEW THAT,
IF YOU MET HIM, YOU'D...

06:00.127 --> 06:01.828
HAVE NO CHOICE.

06:01.862 --> 06:03.330
...SEE THAT
HE WASN'T A THREAT.

06:03.363 --> 06:04.965
I GOT TO GO BACK
TO THE HOUSE

06:04.998 --> 06:06.900
AND CLEAN UP SOME
FUCKING TOE BLOOD.

06:06.934 --> 06:08.435
Woman on P. A.:
<i>DR. LARSON TO 4 WEST.</i>

06:08.468 --> 06:10.237
<i>DR. LARSON TO 4 WEST.</i>

06:11.738 --> 06:15.075
IN KEEPING WITH THE SPIRIT
OF TOMORROW'S LOCAL ELECTIONS,

06:15.108 --> 06:16.410
TONIGHT'S TOPIC WILL BE

06:16.443 --> 06:19.112
"ELECTORAL COLLEGE
vs. POPULAR VOTE."

06:19.146 --> 06:23.817
ADVOCATING THE POPULAR VOTE,
MASTER SHANE BOTWIN.

06:23.851 --> 06:27.054
MY ARGUMENT FOR
THE POPULAR VOTE...

06:28.021 --> 06:30.023
...GEORGE W. BUSH.

06:46.640 --> 06:48.642
BUT THAT'S AGAINST
THE RULES.

06:48.675 --> 06:51.879
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO ARGUE
WHEN HE INVOKES THE NAME

06:51.912 --> 06:53.814
OF THE WORST PRESIDENT
WE'VE EVER HAD

06:53.847 --> 06:55.082
AND THEN JUST SITS?

06:55.115 --> 06:56.550
HE DIDN'T FOLLOW PROTOCOL.

06:56.583 --> 06:58.285
JUST GO, GRETCHEN.

06:58.318 --> 07:02.022
THIS IS TOTALLY UNFAIR.
I FORFEIT.

07:02.055 --> 07:04.925
YOU SUCK!

07:04.958 --> 07:07.027
♪♪ TROUBLE ♪♪

07:08.495 --> 07:11.031
