07:12.633 --> 07:15.002
♪♪ TROUBLE ♪♪

07:18.038 --> 07:19.640
NICE JOB.

07:19.673 --> 07:20.807
IT'S A DISASTER.

07:20.841 --> 07:22.075
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

07:22.109 --> 07:23.844
YOU MADE HER TOTALLY
LOSE HER SHIT.

07:23.877 --> 07:24.878
THAT'S A WIN IN MY BOOK.

07:24.912 --> 07:27.247
I MADE HER HATE ME
EVEN MORE.

07:27.281 --> 07:29.716
OH, MY GOD,
YOU LIKE THAT GIRL?

07:29.750 --> 07:31.919
I LOVE HER.

07:31.952 --> 07:33.187
DOES SHE KNOW?

07:33.220 --> 07:36.423
I'VE NEVER EVEN SPOKEN TO HER.
I'VE ONLY KICKED HER.

07:36.456 --> 07:38.759
WELL,
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT MEANS?

07:38.792 --> 07:40.260
WHAT?

07:40.294 --> 07:41.094
YOU'RE GAY.

07:41.128 --> 07:43.764
SHUT UP. FORGET IT.

07:48.268 --> 07:52.105
ALL RIGHT, SO,
YOU REALLY LIKE THIS GIRL?

07:52.139 --> 07:53.774
HERE'S WHAT YOU DO.

07:53.807 --> 07:55.676
I'VE DONE IT, DAD DID IT,

07:55.709 --> 07:57.144
UNCLE ANDY DOES IT
ALL THE TIME,

07:57.177 --> 07:58.879
AND SOMETIMES
IT EVEN WORKS.

07:58.912 --> 08:00.614
WHAT?

08:00.647 --> 08:01.849
SAY SOMETHING TO HER.

08:01.882 --> 08:03.116
FUCK YOU.

08:03.150 --> 08:04.685
JUST DO IT.
IT'S NOT SO HARD.

08:04.718 --> 08:06.253
EASY FOR YOU TO SAY.

08:06.286 --> 08:08.088
NOT REALLY.

08:08.121 --> 08:09.623
ALL WOMEN ARE EVIL,
LYING BITCHES,

08:09.656 --> 08:11.592
BUT I'M TRYING TO BE
THE GOOD BIG BROTHER HERE,

08:11.625 --> 08:13.527
SO WHEN SHE KICKS THE SHIT
OUT OF YOUR HEART,

08:13.560 --> 08:15.495
I'LL BUY YOU A BEER
WITH MY FAKE I. D.

08:17.297 --> 08:20.434
Celia:
THAT IDIOT IS GOING TO WIN.

08:20.467 --> 08:21.969
PEOPLE LIKE DOUG.

08:22.002 --> 08:23.370
People are stupid.

08:23.403 --> 08:25.405
THEY ELECTED YOU
HEAD OF THE PTA.

08:25.439 --> 08:26.373
OH, PLEASE.

08:26.406 --> 08:29.276
I WAS LIKE HITLER
IN MUNICH.

08:29.309 --> 08:32.779
THOSE DIMWITS WERE JUST ITCHING
FOR SOMEBODY TO FOLLOW.

08:32.813 --> 08:34.581
YOU HAVEN'T LOST YET.

08:34.615 --> 08:35.649
GIVE ME A CLUE.

08:35.682 --> 08:37.050
I LIKE TO DO IT
ALL BY MYSELF.

08:37.084 --> 08:38.785
WANT TO HAVE SEX?

08:38.819 --> 08:44.358
"A SKY‐HIGH ACCESSORY,"
10 LETTERS.

08:44.391 --> 08:46.226
"ORION'S BELT."

08:46.260 --> 08:48.795
OH, SHIT,
THAT'S TOTALLY RIGHT.

08:48.829 --> 08:51.031
OH, WHOOPEE FOR ME.

08:52.833 --> 08:54.801
♪♪ BUH‐BUH BUH BUH ♪♪

08:54.835 --> 08:57.504
THANK YOU.

08:58.906 --> 09:00.374
NANCY?

09:00.407 --> 09:02.776
BACK OFF.

09:02.809 --> 09:05.279
OKAY, I'M SORRY,

09:05.312 --> 09:07.247
AND I HOPE
THAT YOU WON'T LET

09:07.281 --> 09:09.583
THE LITTLE "INCIDENT"
BETWEEN US

09:09.616 --> 09:11.051
RUIN OUR FRIENDSHIP.

09:11.084 --> 09:12.753
I HAVE TO VOTE.

09:12.786 --> 09:16.223
NANCY! MY FRIEND, MY CLIENT.

09:16.256 --> 09:18.458
THANKS FOR SHOWING UP
FOR ME.

09:18.492 --> 09:20.761
I NEED TO REVIEW
THE BOND ISSUES AGAIN.

09:20.794 --> 09:22.763
I'M GOING TO COME BACK
LATER.

09:22.796 --> 09:24.865
SHE'S GOING TO VOTE
FOR YOU.

09:24.898 --> 09:27.501
I'M GOING TO GO
CAST MY BALLOT.

09:27.534 --> 09:28.902
VOTE FOR YOURSELF.

09:28.936 --> 09:30.270
I'D HATE TO SEE YOU
GET SHUT OUT.

09:30.304 --> 09:32.840
MR. WILSON!

09:32.873 --> 09:35.108
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

09:38.312 --> 09:44.218
♪♪ NAH NAH NAH NAH NAH ♪♪

09:46.920 --> 09:48.989
♪♪ NAH NAH NAH ♪♪

09:49.022 --> 09:50.858
WHY ARE YOU SMILING?

09:50.891 --> 09:52.993
OH, JUST WAIT.

09:53.026 --> 09:56.763
WHERE'S MY NAME?
MY NAME'S NOT ON THE BALLOT!

09:56.797 --> 09:58.498
WHAT THE FUCK?!

09:58.532 --> 09:59.700
WHAT DID YOU DO?

09:59.733 --> 10:02.970
NOTHING.
IT'S JUST A MIRACLE.

10:03.003 --> 10:04.905
GOD LOVES ME.

10:04.938 --> 10:06.373
WHERE'S MY NAME?

10:06.406 --> 10:09.042
EXCUSE ME, SIR, ONLY ONE PERSON
ALLOWED IN THE BOOTH AT A TIME.

10:09.076 --> 10:11.178
MY NAME'S NOT ON THE BALLOT.
WHERE'S MY NAME?

10:11.211 --> 10:12.379
WHAT NAME WOULD THAT BE?

10:12.412 --> 10:16.650
DOUG WILSON
OR MR. FUKHUSEN?

10:16.683 --> 10:18.619
YOU'RE RESPONSIBLE
FOR THIS.

10:18.652 --> 10:20.888
I WISH THAT I COULD TAKE CREDIT
FOR THIS ‐‐

10:20.921 --> 10:22.189
I REALLY DO.

10:22.222 --> 10:24.324
DOUG, I'M SURE THERE'S
A REASONABLE EXPLANATION.

10:24.358 --> 10:26.493
YES, YOUR WIFE'S
A CHEATING WHORE.

10:28.495 --> 10:30.597
WRITE ME IN.
DOUG WILSON ‐‐ WRITE ME IN.

10:30.631 --> 10:32.933
WAIT, ARE YOU REALLY GOING
TO LET HIM DO THIS?

10:32.966 --> 10:34.568
MR. WILSON, I'M SORRY.

10:34.601 --> 10:37.271
THERE'S A LAW THAT CLEARLY
PROHIBITS ANY CANDIDATE

10:37.304 --> 10:39.873
FROM CAMPAIGNING WITHIN 300 FEET
OF A POLLING PLACE.

10:39.907 --> 10:41.141
WELL, I'M NOT A CANDIDATE

10:41.175 --> 10:43.310
BECAUSE MY NAME'S NOT ON
THE FUCKING BALLOT, ASSWIPE!

10:43.343 --> 10:45.846
I AM DOUG WILSON,
EVERYBODY!

10:45.879 --> 10:47.514
CHANGE ONLY BRINGS PROBLEMS!

10:47.548 --> 10:48.782
DOUG WILSON!

10:48.815 --> 10:50.184
GET OUT OF HERE.
WRITE ME IN.

10:50.217 --> 10:56.089
295, 296, 297,
298, 299, 300.

10:56.123 --> 10:59.493
VOTE FOR DOUG WILSON,
THE WRITE‐IN CANDIDATE!

10:59.526 --> 11:02.162
CHANGE JUST BRINGS PROBLEMS!
YOU KNOW IT'S TRUE!

11:02.196 --> 11:03.897
DOUG WILSON!
WHO'S YOUR PAL?

11:03.931 --> 11:06.033
DON'T YOU JUST HATE
CELIA HODES?

11:06.066 --> 11:08.168
CELIA HODES HAS CHLAMYDIA!

11:11.872 --> 11:13.740
WHAT'S THAT?

11:13.774 --> 11:15.976
JOB APPLICATIONS.

11:16.009 --> 11:17.511
YOU ALREADY HAVE A JOB.

11:17.544 --> 11:19.112
YES, I DO.

11:19.146 --> 11:21.982
SOON, YOU WILL, TOO.

11:22.015 --> 11:25.018
IF YOU DON'T WANT TO GO
TO COLLEGE, WORK IT IS.

11:25.052 --> 11:26.887
NOT THIS AGAIN.

11:26.920 --> 11:29.923
STARBUCKS, COSTPLUS,

11:29.957 --> 11:32.292
AND BEN & JERRY'S.

11:32.326 --> 11:35.195
AGRESTIC IS JUST BRIMMING
WITH JOB OPPORTUNITIES

11:35.229 --> 11:37.865
FOR A YOUNG MAN
WITH A HIGH‐SCHOOL DIPLOMA.

11:37.898 --> 11:39.933
MOM, WILL YOU SIGN THIS?

11:39.967 --> 11:41.134
WHAT IS IT?

11:41.168 --> 11:44.771
MY LETTER OF RESIGNATION
FROM THE DEBATE TEAM.

11:44.805 --> 11:47.241
OH, THIS IS A PROUD DAY
FOR MOMMY.

11:47.274 --> 11:49.443
WHY ARE YOU QUITTING
THE DEBATE TEAM?

11:49.476 --> 11:50.711
PERSONAL REASONS.

11:50.744 --> 11:52.679
WOULD YOU LIKE TO SHARE
THOSE PERSONAL REASONS?

11:52.713 --> 11:54.181
NO.
DON'T BE SUCH A PUSSY.

11:54.214 --> 11:55.983
JUST GO UP
AND TALK TO HER.

11:56.016 --> 11:57.818
TALK TO WHO?
NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

11:57.851 --> 11:59.820
YOU TWO SHOULD TALK,
MOTHER‐SON.

11:59.853 --> 12:01.021
I'LL CATCH YOU LATER.

12:01.054 --> 12:02.890
SILAS.
LATER, I PROMISE.

12:02.923 --> 12:04.458
WE'LL HAVE A WALK
OR SOMETHING.

12:04.491 --> 12:05.926
I'M GOING TO SCHOOL.

12:05.959 --> 12:08.195
WHO SHOULD YOU TALK TO?

12:08.228 --> 12:11.131
[ SIGHS ]
GRETCHEN.

12:11.164 --> 12:14.868
AND GRETCHEN'S
ON THE DEBATE TEAM?

12:14.902 --> 12:18.472
THAT'S WHY YOU WERE WEARING
DAD'S COLOGNE?

12:18.505 --> 12:20.507
LOOK, I ALREADY WENT
THROUGH THIS WITH SILAS.

12:20.541 --> 12:22.910
I‐I'M JUST GOING TO AVOID HER
FOR THE REST OF THE YEAR.

12:22.943 --> 12:24.411
HEY.

12:24.444 --> 12:27.447
I'M NOT GOING TO LET YOU
OFF THE HOOK LIKE THAT.

12:27.481 --> 12:29.650
YOU HAVE TO BE BRAVE.

12:30.584 --> 12:32.853
I HATED YOUR FATHER
WHEN I FIRST MET HIM.

12:32.886 --> 12:35.489
HE SLEPT ON A FUTON.

12:35.522 --> 12:38.392
HE HAD A GOATEE.

12:38.425 --> 12:42.763
HE HIT ON MY ROOMMATE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:42.796 --> 12:46.433
BUT, OVER TIME,
I GOT TO KNOW HIM,

12:46.466 --> 12:47.634
AND WE FELL IN LOVE.

12:47.668 --> 12:50.270
I'M NOT SAYING YOU AND GRETCHEN
ARE GOING TO FALL IN LOVE.

12:50.304 --> 12:51.839
YOU MIGHT NOT EVEN
LIKE EACH OTHER

12:51.872 --> 12:54.808
IF YOU SPEND TIME TOGETHER,
BUT...

12:54.842 --> 12:57.811
YOU HAVE TO GIVE IT A SHOT.

12:57.845 --> 13:01.014
WHY DO YOU ALWAYS
HAVE TO BRING UP DAD?

13:07.387 --> 13:09.489
[ SIGHS ]

13:09.523 --> 13:10.490
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

13:10.524 --> 13:11.792
Andy: YAEL.

13:11.825 --> 13:13.093
SHALOM.

13:13.126 --> 13:14.795
HOW'S MY LITTLE MAN?

13:14.828 --> 13:16.763
OW, GOD!

13:16.797 --> 13:18.832
UH, SORRY, SHOOTING PAINS.

13:18.866 --> 13:20.234
DIDN'T THEY GIVE YOU
MEDICATION?

13:20.267 --> 13:21.902
OH, I DON'T BELIEVE
IN PAINKILLERS.

13:21.935 --> 13:22.970
THEY'RE ADDICTIVE, YOU KNOW.

13:23.003 --> 13:26.640
WHAT CAN I DO
TO MAKE YOU FEEL BETTER?

13:26.673 --> 13:28.675
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

13:28.709 --> 13:31.345
HOW ABOUT LETTING ME PITCH
INSTEAD OF CATCH THIS TIME?

13:31.378 --> 13:32.913
HMM.

13:32.946 --> 13:39.286
♪♪ BUH, BUH, BUM ♪♪

13:39.319 --> 13:44.892
♪♪ BUH, BUH, BUM ♪♪
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

13:44.925 --> 13:49.663
♪♪ BUH, BUH, BUM ♪♪

13:49.696 --> 13:52.099
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

13:53.433 --> 13:55.569
HELLO?

13:55.602 --> 13:56.904
HI, SID.

13:56.937 --> 13:59.706
THANK YOU.

14:01.475 --> 14:06.213
IT CAME DOWN TO THREE
LOUSY VOTES ‐‐

14:06.246 --> 14:09.716
THREE FUCKING,
LOUSY VOTES.

14:09.750 --> 14:11.919
HE WASN'T EVEN
ON THE FUCKING BALLOT.

14:11.952 --> 14:14.054
YOU'LL GET HIM
NEXT TIME, TIGER.

14:14.087 --> 14:17.224
THERE'S NOT GOING TO BE
A NEXT TIME.

14:17.257 --> 14:18.091
I WON.

14:18.125 --> 14:20.861
WAH! WAH?! AAH!

14:20.894 --> 14:22.829
[ LAUGHING ]

14:22.863 --> 14:26.300
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

14:26.333 --> 14:27.901
HELLO?

14:27.935 --> 14:30.370
I'LL KEEP MY CONCESSION
SPEECH SHORT.

14:30.404 --> 14:31.205
FUCK YOU.

14:31.238 --> 14:32.472
WOW, THAT'S BRILLIANT.

14:32.506 --> 14:35.008
APPARENTLY, MY HUSBAND
IS ALSO YOUR SPEECHWRITER.

14:35.042 --> 14:36.677
NO, I CAME UP WITH THAT ONE
ALL BY MYSELF.

14:36.710 --> 14:38.846
I EVEN HAVE IT MEMORIZED.
YOU WANT TO HEAR IT AGAIN?

14:38.879 --> 14:39.780
FUCK YOU! FUCK YOU!

14:39.813 --> 14:42.416
FUCK YOU!

14:42.449 --> 14:44.418
LOSER.

14:45.953 --> 14:47.588
SPEECH!

14:48.956 --> 14:50.591
SPEECH!

14:51.892 --> 14:55.229
I WON.
I FUCKING WON.

14:55.262 --> 14:57.030
AAH!

14:57.064 --> 14:59.333
[ LAUGHS ]

15:01.201 --> 15:03.670
THAT WAS NOT BAD...

15:03.704 --> 15:05.272
FOR A SKINNY GIMP.

15:05.305 --> 15:07.808
I FOUND YOUR GIMLET SPOTS,
DIDN'T I?

15:07.841 --> 15:09.877
[ CHUCKLES ]

15:09.910 --> 15:13.280
HEY, WAIT, WAIT!
HANG OUT.

15:13.313 --> 15:15.048
I THOUGHT MAYBE
WE'D GO AGAIN.

15:15.082 --> 15:16.683
I HAVE A LIFE, YOU KNOW.

15:16.717 --> 15:19.753
I CAN'T SPEND ALL DAY IN BED,
LIKE SOME PEOPLE.

15:19.786 --> 15:22.189
OKAY, OKAY.
[ CHUCKLES ]

15:22.222 --> 15:24.358
WELL,
WILL YOU COME BY LATER?

15:24.391 --> 15:26.860
I HAVE A LOT OF WORK
AT SCHOOL.

15:26.894 --> 15:29.530
WHEN DO YOU THINK
YOU'LL BE BACK?

15:29.563 --> 15:30.831
EVERYONE MISSES YOU.

15:30.864 --> 15:33.467
YEAH, ABOUT THAT.

15:33.500 --> 15:36.470
I THINK GOD HAS A DIFFERENT
PLAN FOR ME.

15:36.503 --> 15:39.072
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

15:39.106 --> 15:41.208
I'M SAYING, NOW THAT
I'M PARTIALLY TOELESS,

15:41.241 --> 15:44.044
THERE'S NO WAY I CAN BE SENT
TO IRAQ,

15:44.077 --> 15:47.014
SO I'M THINKING, GOD WANTS ME
TO DO SOMETHING ELSE

15:47.047 --> 15:48.682
BESIDES STUDY
FOR THE RABBINATE.

15:48.715 --> 15:52.252
I'M THINKING MAYBE HE WANTS ME
TO OPEN A MICROBREWERY

15:52.286 --> 15:55.789
OR...DAY‐TRADE
IN OIL FUTURES.

15:55.822 --> 15:58.892
YOU CAN'T COMMIT TO ANYTHING,
CAN YOU?

15:58.926 --> 16:00.227
DON'T SAY THAT.

16:00.260 --> 16:01.929
I'M COMMITTED TO YOU.

16:01.962 --> 16:03.864
NOTHING IS CHANGING
BETWEEN US.

16:03.897 --> 16:04.932
OW!

16:04.965 --> 16:06.200
I TRUSTED YOU.

16:06.233 --> 16:08.468
I PUT MY JOB ON THE LINE.

16:08.502 --> 16:10.037
I THOUGHT YOU HAD RUACH.

16:10.070 --> 16:12.739
I HAVE TONS OF RUACH!

16:12.773 --> 16:15.242
I'M FILLED WITH IT!

16:15.275 --> 16:16.810
"NO RUACH."

16:16.844 --> 16:20.514
YOU SCRAWNY,
SELFISH LITTLE PIG.

16:20.547 --> 16:22.416
I DID EVERYTHING FOR YOU!

16:22.449 --> 16:23.884
GOD! FUCK!

16:23.917 --> 16:25.018
QUIT IT.

16:25.052 --> 16:28.121
THAT DOG SHOULD HAVE BITTEN
YOUR DICK OFF!

16:29.957 --> 16:31.491
YAEL!

16:31.525 --> 16:32.492
YAEL!

16:32.526 --> 16:33.794
SHIT!

16:33.827 --> 16:34.928
Doug: WHO AM I?

16:34.962 --> 16:37.931
YESTERDAY I WAS COUNCILMAN DOUG.

16:37.965 --> 16:39.933
I COULD PARK ANYWHERE.

16:39.967 --> 16:41.969
I HAD CUTSIES IN EVERY LINE ‐‐

16:42.002 --> 16:44.371
THE BANK, THE MOVIE THEATER.

16:44.404 --> 16:46.507
HOP FONG'S.

16:46.540 --> 16:49.543
THEY GAVE ME THE THREE‐ITEM
COMBO FOR THE PRICE OF TWO.

16:50.811 --> 16:54.448
I GOT TO DRIVE THE FIRE TRUCK.

16:54.481 --> 16:56.984
AND NOW...

16:57.017 --> 16:58.385
I GOT NOTHING.

16:58.418 --> 16:59.353
ZILCH, NADA.

16:59.386 --> 17:01.755
I'M JUST ANOTHER
CERTIFIED PUBLIC ASSHOLE.

17:01.788 --> 17:03.891
I'M SORRY, DOUG.

17:03.924 --> 17:05.459
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

17:05.492 --> 17:07.127
ACTUALLY IT IS.

17:08.228 --> 17:10.797
I NEVER FILED YOUR
INTENT‐TO‐RUN PAPERS.

17:10.831 --> 17:13.066
THEY WERE ON MY DESK
AT WORK.

17:13.100 --> 17:15.636
I‐I HAD THEM ALL FILLED OUT
AND READY TO GO,

17:15.669 --> 17:16.803
BUT THEN I GOT FIRED,

17:16.837 --> 17:19.306
AND I THREW THEM INTO A BOX
WHEN I CLEARED OUT MY OFFICE.

17:19.339 --> 17:21.275
AND THEN I GOT TAZERED
AND I...

17:21.308 --> 17:23.977
I GUESS I JUST FORGOT
ABOUT THEM.

17:25.479 --> 17:29.349
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY.
I AM REALLY SORRY.

17:31.919 --> 17:32.953
OW!

17:32.986 --> 17:33.954
WHAT?

17:33.987 --> 17:36.056
I SAID I WAS SORRY.

17:36.089 --> 17:38.992
I COMPLETELY FUCKED UP,

17:39.026 --> 17:41.895
BUT NOW IT IS TIME FOR US
TO PULL OURSELVES TOGETHER

17:41.929 --> 17:44.398
AND DO SOME SERIOUS
SOUL‐SEARCHING.

17:44.431 --> 17:46.099
OW! JESUS!

17:46.133 --> 17:47.100
YOU FUCKED UP.

17:47.134 --> 17:48.669
WHY DO I HAVE TO
SOUL‐SEARCH?

17:48.702 --> 17:50.103
YOU'VE RUINED MY LIFE.

17:50.137 --> 17:52.673
GET THE FUCK
OUT OF MY OFFICE.

17:54.341 --> 17:55.776
I'VE GOT POT.

17:55.809 --> 17:56.777
AMAZING POT.

17:56.810 --> 17:59.246
GET OUT OF MY OFFICE.

18:12.459 --> 18:15.362
SO, HERE WE ARE.
WHAT'S YOUR PLAN?

18:15.395 --> 18:16.864
I WANT IN.

18:16.897 --> 18:18.232
IN ON WHAT?

18:18.265 --> 18:20.033
I WANT US TO DO THIS
TOGETHER.

18:20.067 --> 18:21.969
I THINK WE WOULD BE GOOD
TOGETHER.

18:22.002 --> 18:23.604
ARE WE GONNA START A BAND?

18:23.637 --> 18:25.105
I WANT TO HELP YOU
SELL POT.

18:25.138 --> 18:27.140
NO. NO WAY. NEXT PLAN.

18:27.174 --> 18:28.442
THERE IS NO NEXT PLAN.

18:28.475 --> 18:30.444
I CAN'T GET INTO
A DECENT SCHOOL.

18:30.477 --> 18:33.614
I'M NOT WORKING AT STARBUCKS
JERKING LATTES FOR MINIMUM WAGE,

18:33.647 --> 18:36.316
SO IT'S THE ONLY THING
THAT REALLY MAKES SENSE.

18:36.350 --> 18:37.551
I'LL TELL YOU
WHAT MAKES SENSE ‐‐

18:37.584 --> 18:39.920
GOING TO A JUNIOR COLLEGE,
DOING WELL,

18:39.953 --> 18:42.155
TRANSFERRING TO A DECENT
UNIVERSITY MAKES SENSE.

18:42.189 --> 18:44.324
FACE IT, NANCY,
I'M NO GENIUS.

18:44.358 --> 18:47.995
I'M NOT GONNA GROW UP AND BE
A DOCTOR OR A LAWYER,

18:48.028 --> 18:50.631
BUT I AM GOOD
AT OTHER THINGS,

18:50.664 --> 18:52.032
AND I COULD HELP YOU.

18:52.065 --> 18:53.901
SILAS, I WILL NEVER,
EVER, EVER

18:53.934 --> 18:55.669
LET YOU GET INVOLVED
IN WHAT I DO.

18:55.702 --> 18:57.271
I JUST WON'T!
I ALREADY AM INVOLVED.

18:57.304 --> 18:58.739
THIS CONVERSATION IS OVER.

18:58.772 --> 19:00.908
YOU'RE SUCH A FUCKING
HYPOCRITE.

19:00.941 --> 19:03.010
YES, I AM.
SO LIVE WITH IT.

19:03.043 --> 19:05.245
YOU KNOW, YOU THINK
YOU'RE PROTECTING ME,

19:05.279 --> 19:08.148
BUT YOU'RE NOT PROTECTING ME
FROM A GODDAMN THING.

19:10.150 --> 19:11.718
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

19:15.289 --> 19:17.724
WHOA‐HO!

19:19.960 --> 19:21.595
SWEET‐‐ NANCY.

19:21.628 --> 19:22.696
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:22.729 --> 19:23.797
Wait, darling.

19:23.830 --> 19:25.299
UH...

19:25.332 --> 19:27.801
OH, GOD. UH, NANCY,
I LEFT YOU A MESSAGE.

19:27.835 --> 19:29.736
WHAT DID IT SAY?
Tim: HI.

19:29.770 --> 19:32.806
IT SAID THAT,
UH, I HAVE TIM.

19:32.840 --> 19:35.642
I HAVE MY SON TONIGHT.

19:35.676 --> 19:38.145
YES, TIM. HI, TIM.

19:38.178 --> 19:39.279
WHAT'S SHE DOING HERE?

19:39.313 --> 19:41.281
I THOUGHT IT WAS JUST
GOING TO BE US.

19:41.315 --> 19:42.749
DON'T BE RUDE.

19:42.783 --> 19:44.751
I'M SORRY.

19:44.785 --> 19:46.753
BAD TIMING.
I SHOULD BE GOING.

19:46.787 --> 19:48.655
NICE TO SEE YOU
AGAIN, TIM.

19:48.689 --> 19:49.790
PETER, I'LL CALL YOU.

19:49.823 --> 19:51.024
NO, NO, NO.
YOU SHOULD STAY.

19:51.058 --> 19:53.694
TIM AND I WERE JUST GOING
TO PLAY A GAME

19:53.727 --> 19:55.495
OF "CARCASS" OR SOMETHING.

19:55.529 --> 19:58.098
CARCASSONNE ‐‐ IT'S INSPIRED
BY THE MEDIEVAL TOWN

19:58.131 --> 20:00.067
OF CARCASSONNE
IN SOUTHERN FRANCE,

20:00.100 --> 20:02.669
WHICH IS FAMOUS FOR
ITS FORMIDABLE CITY WALLS ‐‐

20:02.703 --> 20:04.238
THAT SOUNDS SO EXCITING.

20:04.271 --> 20:05.572
YOU DIDN'T EVEN
LET ME EXPLAIN.

20:05.606 --> 20:09.543
I‐I'M JUST NOT REALLY
VERY GOOD AT GAMES.

20:09.576 --> 20:12.946
WELL, MY MOM IS. I GUESS
SHE'S A LOT SMARTER THAN YOU.

20:12.980 --> 20:15.616
I WOULDN'T DOUBT THAT
FOR A SECOND.

20:15.649 --> 20:18.151
GO SET UP THE GAME.
THANKS.

20:18.185 --> 20:19.820
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

20:19.853 --> 20:20.954
SORRY.

20:20.988 --> 20:22.322
NO, IT'S MY FAULT.

20:22.356 --> 20:23.590
I SHOULD HAVE CHECKED
MY MESSAGES.

20:23.624 --> 20:25.626
HE GOES BACK TO HIS MOM
IN THE MORNING.

20:25.659 --> 20:26.627
DINNER TOMORROW NIGHT?

20:26.660 --> 20:28.328
GREAT.

20:28.362 --> 20:30.931
DAD! ARE WE GONNA PLAY
OR NOT?

20:30.964 --> 20:32.833
JUST A SEC!

20:32.866 --> 20:36.470
You're twice as smart
as his mom.

20:46.547 --> 20:48.282
CONRAD.

20:49.883 --> 20:52.386
CAN I JOIN YOU?

20:52.419 --> 20:53.921
IT'S YOUR HOUSE.

20:53.954 --> 20:55.923
IT'S YOURS, TOO.

20:55.956 --> 20:58.091
NO, I'M JUST
THE NIGHT WATCHMAN.

20:58.926 --> 21:00.727
YOU'RE MY PARTNER.

21:00.761 --> 21:03.030
WHATEVER YOU
WANT TO CALL ME.

21:09.636 --> 21:10.737
I CAME HERE ‐‐

21:10.771 --> 21:14.408
HOW IS IT I CAN LIVE
FOR 36 YEARS,

21:14.441 --> 21:16.643
PACK EVERYTHING THAT'S
IMPORTANT TO ME,

21:16.677 --> 21:18.812
AND FIT IT
INTO A DUFFEL BAG?

21:18.846 --> 21:21.815
YOU PACKED A DUFFEL BAG?

21:21.849 --> 21:24.718
IT'S IN MY CAR RIGHT NOW.

21:24.751 --> 21:26.186
I CAME HERE TO SAY ‐‐

21:26.220 --> 21:27.955
YOU CAME TO SAY
YOU'RE SORRY AGAIN.

21:27.988 --> 21:30.457
YOU CAN STILL WALK AWAY
IF YOU WANT.

21:30.490 --> 21:34.895
NANCY, DON'T TAKE ME TO DINNER
WITH YOUR HUSBAND ONE NIGHT,

21:34.928 --> 21:37.464
AND THEN TELL ME I CAN WALK
THE NEXT.

21:37.497 --> 21:38.765
I KNOW I CAN WALK.

21:38.799 --> 21:41.101
I KNOW THAT.

21:50.477 --> 21:54.381
ARE YOU...GONNA WALK?

21:54.414 --> 21:57.818
I'D BE ALL ALONE.

21:57.851 --> 22:00.120
YOU GOT YOUR HUSBAND.

22:00.153 --> 22:03.790
IT'S A BUSINESS
ARRANGEMENT.

22:03.824 --> 22:06.894
YOU GOT YOUR FRIENDS.

22:06.927 --> 22:08.695
YOUR KIDS.

22:10.130 --> 22:12.733
SHIT, I GOT A FUCKING
DUFFEL BAG.

22:12.766 --> 22:14.701
SOMETIMES I WISH
THAT'S ALL I HAD.

22:14.735 --> 22:15.702
NO, YOU DON'T.

22:15.736 --> 22:17.738
SOMETIMES.

22:17.771 --> 22:20.374
I LOVE MY KIDS.

22:20.407 --> 22:22.342
I LOVE MY KIDS
MORE THAN ANYTHING,

22:22.376 --> 22:26.213
BUT SOMETIMES I THINK
WHAT IT WOULD HAVE BEEN LIKE

22:26.246 --> 22:28.448
IF THEY DIED
WHEN JUDAH DIED.

22:28.482 --> 22:33.086
WHAT IT WOULD BE LIKE
NOT TO HAVE TO WORRY.

22:33.120 --> 22:36.823
TO BE ONLY RESPONSIBLE
FOR ME...

22:36.857 --> 22:39.893
AND FREE.

22:39.927 --> 22:42.429
How nice...

22:42.462 --> 22:44.298
that might feel.

22:46.633 --> 22:49.603
HOW HORRIBLE IS THAT?

22:50.938 --> 22:55.642
I'M AN...AWFUL...

22:55.676 --> 22:58.078
HORRIBLE PERSON.

23:03.750 --> 23:05.586
[ SIGHS ]

23:12.192 --> 23:15.662
[ Laughing ]
I CAN'T GO HOME STONED.

23:15.696 --> 23:16.563
IT'S OKAY.

23:16.597 --> 23:18.765
I CAN'T BE STONED
IN FRONT OF MY KIDS.

23:18.799 --> 23:19.833
TWO HOURS.

23:19.867 --> 23:21.001
YOU'LL BE CLEAN
IN TWO HOURS.

23:21.034 --> 23:22.903
THIS SHIT'S GONNA HAVE
YOUR NAME ON IT.

23:22.936 --> 23:24.705
IT WOULD BE KIND OF WEIRD
NOT TO TRY IT.

23:26.707 --> 23:29.142
AT LEAST ONCE.

23:39.786 --> 23:41.755
I LOVE MY KIDS.

23:41.788 --> 23:43.657
I KNOW YOU DO.

23:43.690 --> 23:45.025
THEY'RE MY LIFE.

23:51.431 --> 23:54.635
ONE HIT TAKES THE SHIT
AND ROLLS IT BACK.

23:54.668 --> 23:56.937
TWO...

23:56.970 --> 23:59.273
TAKES IT OUT THE HOUSE.

24:17.057 --> 24:19.693
YOU PACKED A DUFFEL BAG?

24:23.697 --> 24:26.767
IF I WAS GOING,
I'D BE GONE.

24:31.939 --> 24:35.075
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO
FOR TWO HOURS?

24:51.825 --> 24:53.827
WATCH THE GRASS GROW...

24:53.861 --> 24:55.662
LITERALLY.

24:59.499 --> 25:00.667
[ SNIFFLES ]

25:00.701 --> 25:02.336
SOUNDS LIKE FUN.

25:02.369 --> 25:04.037
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:05.906 --> 25:07.407
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

25:07.441 --> 25:08.642
DEAN?

25:08.675 --> 25:11.812
YES, COUNCILWOMAN HODES?

25:11.845 --> 25:15.649
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO STOP
SMOKING POT.

25:17.417 --> 25:21.021
I CAN'T HAVE YOU
GETTING BUSTED.

25:21.054 --> 25:26.560
I AM MAKING AGRESTIC
A DRUG‐FREE ZONE.

25:35.035 --> 25:37.471
WARN YOUR DEALER.

25:40.274 --> 25:43.310
♪♪ MIND YOUR MOTHERFUCKIN'
BUSINESS ♪♪

25:43.343 --> 25:45.479
♪♪ AND LET THEM SMOKE! ♪♪

25:45.512 --> 25:48.682
♪♪ I DON'T WANNA HAVE TO BUST
YOUR MOTHERFUCKIN' HEAD ♪♪

25:48.715 --> 25:51.351
♪♪ I DON'T WANNA HAVE TO STAND
ON THE CORNER IN THE BUSHES ♪♪

25:51.385 --> 25:53.020
♪♪ AND BEING WITH THE INFRARED ♪♪

25:53.053 --> 25:54.555
♪♪ I DON'T WANNA HAVE TO
DUCK THE FEDS ♪♪

25:54.588 --> 25:56.790
♪♪ I DON'T WANNA HAVE TO DUCK
WHEN I'M GETTIN' BREAD ♪♪

25:56.823 --> 25:59.226
♪♪ I DON'T WANNA HAVE TO FILL
YOUR WHORE ASS UP WITH LEAD ♪♪

25:59.259 --> 26:00.694
♪♪ I DON'T WANNA HAVE TO SEE
NO POPO'S ♪♪

26:00.727 --> 26:02.629
♪♪ MOTHERFUCKERS ALWAYS KNOCKING
AT MY DOOR ♪♪

26:02.663 --> 26:04.097
♪♪ AND I GOTTA HAVE
THE 44 ANTIDOTE ♪♪

26:04.131 --> 26:05.899
♪♪ NOW I GOTTA GO AHEAD
AND GO SMOKE ♪♪

26:05.933 --> 26:07.568
♪♪ 'CAUSE MY MAN IS GOING
IN THE ZONE ♪♪

26:07.601 --> 26:09.002
[ RAPPING INDISTINCTLY ]

26:09.036 --> 26:10.838
♪♪ MOTHERFUCKER GOTTA LET ME
